13
00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Fast-paced and exciting.

14
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
The NBA features players who are global icons.

15
00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Some teams might come out of nowhere and surprise everyone.

16
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
How do you play it?

17
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.000
Teams aim to shoot the ball into the opposing team's basket.

18
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:05.000
The team with the most points after four quarters wins.

19
00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:11.000
USA's basketball top three players are LeBron James, Stephen Curry, and A'ja Riyadh Wilson.

20
00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:12.000
