23
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
How do you play it?

24
00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:29.000
Players hit a ball and run around four bases to score runs.

25
00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:32.000
The team with the most runs wins.

26
00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:38.000
USA's baseball top three players are Jennie Finch, Babe Ruth, and Derek Jeter.

27
00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:40.000
Fourth place, ice hockey.

28
00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:44.000
