36
00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:13.000
How do you play it?

37
00:02:13.000 --> 00:02:17.000
Teams try to score by kicking a ball into the opponent's net.

38
00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:21.000
The team with the most goals wins.

39
00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:26.000
USA's soccer top three players are Lionel Messi, Christian Pulisic, and Clint Dempsey.

40
